################################
QoMMMa Installation Instructions
R. Lonsdale Nov 2012
################################

To install QoMMMa, you need a fortran compiler (in this case f77, although compilation with other compilers should be possible).

Starting in this directory, type the following:

cd src
make
cd freq
make
cd ../tinker
./qommma_compile.make
./qommma_library.make
./qommma_link.make
cp analyze_qommma.x ../../bin/analyze_grad
cp minimize_qommma.x ../../bin/minimize
cd ../../

You will then need to change the QOMMMA variable in the file qommma, to reflect the currect directory.
